{"tid":710660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大眾哥哥、正義撚、幫阿婆執紙皮、嘅大台當紅小生馬仔-馬駿偉赤裸上陣，令一眾女士濕如決隄","createTime":"2018-06-21T02:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T09:05:01.000Z","uid":71166,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b576873916007d0110565186661f49cb5cd5997","tid":710660,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/100620_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F100620_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=2b1dc93b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大眾哥哥、正義撚、幫阿婆執紙皮、嘅大台當紅小生馬仔-我偉深知咩叫神秘感，show少少用放大鏡先睇到嘅肌肉，再用一個90年代初影相必用手勢三寶之一「👍」，唔講真係以為初出度影落呀<br />\n<br />\n為咗加啲可愛感，我偉特意加上豬鼻同心心外框，十足十2000年MK仔影嘅貼紙相質素呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「來懷念錯對！來懷念過去！曾結義阿妹日子總有樂趣！法拉不會絕望！嘉欣不會躊躇！阿怡夢裏競爭每日拼命進取！！！」</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3dcb98d4ffcee141e1299b280ff083125205ec56","tid":710660,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://singimap.com/artiste/portfolio/417/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsingimap.com%2Fartiste%2Fportfolio%2F417%2F1.jpg&h=4f3eb5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a24524edfe773caef707ba84cff91859120e98e","tid":710660,"uid":22743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c